snippet.title: Hopeless: The Dark Cave - Trailer
snippet.description:
New Game by the creators of Hopeless - Ruby Run: Eye God's Revenge.
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.upopa.rubyrun

Hopeless is a cute and loveable survival horror game.
Don't let the blobs get too scared or the'll kill themselves!

Available on Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.upopa.hopeless
Coming soon to iOS

Made by Upopa Games Ltd.
See upcoming games at www.upopa.com
